St. John’s Basketball Coach Steve Lavin Treated for Early Prostate Cancer

-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 
2011-04-08T16:09:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/st-john-s-basketball-coach-steve-lavin-treated-for-early-prostate-cancer.html
St. John’s University basketball
coach Steve Lavin will undergo treatment for an early stage of
prostate cancer, the school said in a press release.  A complete cure is expected, his urologist, Jonathan
Schiff, said in the release, and Lavin will not miss time from
coaching.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eben Novywilliams in New York at 
 enovywilliam@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net  